    "title": "Aastha RT 9/F",
    "body": "Name: HARNE AASTHA MUKUND (Aastha):   Email: aharne2-c@my. cityu. edu. hk: Responsible Floor: 9/F: Greetings from Aastha, your Residence Tutor on the 9th floor! I hope you‚Äôre all excited about the upcoming hall experiences. As the Residence Tutor, my goal is to create a disciplined and enjoyable living environment for all of us. I‚Äôm also thrilled to serve as the Advocacy RT, responsible for the social media and Publicity team. I want to express my sincere appreciation for your incredible support and enthusiasm. Our hall activities are always in full swing, thanks to everyone‚Äôs energy and dedication. The 9th floor, our girls‚Äô floor, is a wonderful mix of residents from different countries and academic backgrounds. It‚Äôs amazing to see the talent and friendliness that each of you brings to our community. Whether it‚Äôs sharing snacks or enjoying a pizza night in the hall, or cooking together, every moment spent together is cherished and valued. I wish you all a colourful and memorable residential life this year. Let‚Äôs continue to embrace the JCAC spirit and support one another in our journey. "
